{
  "stem": "27340.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Just we had couples that were obviously very much going together, and they would, you know, go out for a walk in the evening or something of that sort.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But you know, in the house, in the building itself, it was 100% clean.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We never had any problems whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I wonder what under present circumstances such a close knit community would actually achieve or otherwise fail to achieve under the present circumstances.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And after that, since I was already registered somehow with the Haganah.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They showed interest in my joining the armed forces in Israel, and so I went to Israel after exactly one year's full rotation on the farm, which was a wonderful experience.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I loved every minute of it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I went to the army, and the army in Israel had a specific unit which was known as Cheil Mada, the Scientific Corps, which consisted fundamentally of engineers, physicists, chemists, mathematicians who were engaged in development of weaponry.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And my function, I was not a qualified engineer at that stage, but I'd had practical experience as an apprentice tool maker.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And this came in useful in so far that after you designed and modified certain things, they after all had to be made as well.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And so we had to form a-- a-- a-- a-- a-- a-- a-- workshop, a factory.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was between Haifa and Akko in Haifa Bay.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was not too far away from a village that was called Kiryat Ata, where Ata was a major textile manufacturer, and very close to a kibbutz that was named after the Czech president Masaryk.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was called Kfar Masaryk.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We're now in 1949, '50, '51, '52.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm 71, nearly 71.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, then.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, let's go back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Born '26.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
